VATICAN CITY, Vatican, May 30, 2022/APO Group/ --
                                                        
                            Apostolic Journey of His Holiness Pope Francis to the Democratic Republic of Congo and South Sudan (Ecumenical Peace Pilgrimage to the South Sudanese Land and People) - 2 to 7 July 2022 – Programme, 28.05.2022:



Saturday, 2 July 2022

ROME - KINSHASA



09:30

Departure by airplane from Rome/Fiumicino International Airport to Kinshasa



16:00

Arrival at Kinshasa International Airport



16:00

OFFICIAL WELCOME at Kinshasa "Ndjili" International Airport



17:30

WELCOME CEREMONY at the "Palais de la Nation" in Kinshasa



17:45

COURTESY VISIT TO THE PRESIDENT OF THE REPUBLIC in the "Salle Présidentielle" of the "Palais de la Nation" in Kinshasa



18:30

MEETING WITH AUTHORITIES AND THE DIPLOMATIC CORPS in the garden of the "Palais de la Nation" in Kinshasa

Address of the Holy Father



19:15

PRIVATE MEETING WITH THE MEMBERS OF THE SOCIETY OF JESUS in the Apostolic Nunciature in Kinshasa





Sunday, 3 July 2022

KINSHASA  



08:00

HOLY MASS at Ndolo Airport in Kinshasa

Homily of the Holy Father

Angelus



18:00

MEETING WITH BISHOPS, PRIESTS, RELIGIOUS, CONSECRATED PERSONS, SEMINARIANS in the Cathedral "Notre Dame du Congo" in Kinshasa

Address of the Holy Father



