MEETING WITH THE VICEPRESIDENTS OF THE REPUBLIC at the Presidential Palace in Juba



17:00

MEETING WITH AUTHORITIES, CIVIL SOCIETY AND THE DIPLOMATIC CORPS in the garden of the Presidential Palace in Juba

Address of the Holy Father





